title: Photograph, "Covered Box with Foliate Design on Lid"
description: A deep container with a rounded bottom and a shallow lid comprise the box, which appears to be fabricated from a metallic material. Decorative features are a narrow, ruffled band encircling the lip of the lid and a foliate motif centered on top. The orject served as packaing material for an unspecified product, perhaps cosmetic.
